(12, 8, 'Dave', 'A veritable blitz of flavour hit my mouth when tasting this! Absolutely loved it.', '2015-03-29 14:44:08'),
(14, 8, 'Julie', 'Very salty. If I do it again I''ll use less soy and try a different cheese.', '2015-05-04 19:44:32'),
(15, 11, 'Jonty', 'Very nice indeed. I won''t be going back to Dominos for a while!', '2015-05-05 20:32:41'),
(16, 12, 'Tex', 'I think this is more of a Quesadilla because of the presence of the cheese.', '2015-05-09 13:27:57'),
(17, 12, 'Chef', 'No way! This is definitely an Enchilada because it has beef inside.', '2015-05-09 13:28:57'),
(18, 12, 'Alice', 'I can tell you that it is definitely not a Burrito because beans is what makes a Burrito a Burrito. Along with rice.', '2015-05-09 13:30:30'),
(19, 12, 'Pablo', 'Do not worry too much about the name, it tastes great whatever you call it!', '2015-05-09 20:56:48'),
(20, 12, 'Mavis', 'Which cheese did you use?', '2015-05-09 21:00:19'),
(21, 12, 'Pete', 'Hi Mavis, we used grated mature cheddar. But any strong cheese will do!', '2015-05-09 21:03:06'),
(22, 12, 'Andy', 'I used Red Leicester, worked out very well.', '2015-05-09 21:20:51'),
(23, 8, 'Manuel', 'This should definitely be standard street food around the world!', '2015-05-10 09:34:31'),
(24, 1, 'Jackie', 'I can''t believe how much this tastes like the proper Wagamama recipe!', '2015-05-13 19:05:03'),
(25, 2, 'Il cibo', 'Loved the first two sauces!', '2015-05-13 19:13:45'),
(28, 13, 'Alan P', 'Lovely stuff', '2015-05-16 15:59:19');

